             was indicted for <rs id="t18320216-40-off215" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320216-40-off215" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320216-40-off215" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18320216-40-cd216" type="crimeDate">8th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320216-40-off215 t18320216-40-cd216"></join>, 6 shillings, 1 sixpence, and 6d. in copper monies
            </rs>, the monies of 
               
                  <persName id="t18320216-40-victim402" type="victimName">
                     Abraham 
                     Holwell
                  <interp inst="t18320216-40-victim402" type="surname" value="Holwell"></interp>
